QuestData.Title: Caretaker Caice
QuestData.Description: I am done with you. There are, however, others who can use your aid.$b$bCaretaker Caice, standing on that stump behind me, can probably give you another assignment. You should speak with him now.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Caretaker Caice at the Deathknell Graves in Tirisfal Glades.
QuestData.RewardText: Yes? And who might you be?
